data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning single-family residence boasts a custom kitchen, perfect for culinary adventures. Step onto solid poured epoxy floors that exude modern elegance throughout. Dive into luxury with a refreshing pool, while soaking in serene water views. With 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, it's ideal for families or hosting guests. Nestled in a highly sought-after neighborhood with no HOA, enjoy your own backyard paradise! Updated gas water heater and A/C in 2017 ensure comfort year-round. Don't miss out on this slice of heaven!
